Author: Tiny_Buttercups98
Text: Guys none of you are ugly. You've just gotten so used to yourself you no longer see the beauty.  Like myself, I've spent so long analysing my stupid face that I hate it to it's very core.  You are not ugly, you've just gotten used to your beauty as cheesy as it sounds and you might not believe it because I am just some weirdo on the internet.

Author: umsooooyeah
Text: Ugly, fat and scary people unite
